### Get all tickets
GET http://localhost:4004/incident/Tickets
Accept: application/json

### Get single ticket (use ID from above response)
GET http://localhost:4004/incident/Tickets?$top=1
Accept: application/json

### Embed all tickets (run this FIRST to enable similarity search)
POST http://localhost:4004/incident/embedAllTickets
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### AI Categorization (replace ticketID with actual ID number)
POST http://localhost:4004/incident/categorizeTicket
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ticketID": 1
}

### Generate AI Response
POST http://localhost:4004/incident/generateResponse
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ticketID": 1
}

### Find Similar Tickets (RAG)
POST http://localhost:4004/incident/findSimilarTickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ticketID": 1
}

### Open Fiori UI
# Navigate to: http://localhost:4004/incidents/webapp/index.html